sh to buy goods this season. Owing not only to general\nbusiness depression, but to local conditions as well, our recent invoice shows more stock on hand than we have ever\nhad had at any previous season. These must be converted into money, hence these remarkable reductions:\nSuits at half price\nWe have about 35 sample stiits, all the latest styles\nand the highest quality, which we are going to close\nout at HALF PRICE, Don't miss this line,\n15.00 suits at 7.50 25.00 soils at $12.50\n18.50 suits at 9.25 30.00 suits at 15.00\n22.00 suits at 11.00 35.00 suits at 17.50\nSuits\n75 ladies and misses suits, all new styles, made\nof imported French Serge and imported Scotch\nTweeds colors black, blue, green and novelties.\nAll sizes. Regular prices 25.00 to $42.50\n$12.50, $14.50, $16.50,\n$18.50, $22.50, $24.50\n150 Skirts\nColors black, blue, brown, champagne, gray. All\nmade of fine imported materials, strictly man tailored.\n$3.98, $5.98, $6.98, $7.98,\n^$8.98, $9.98, $12.98, $14.98\nbe cleaned up and turned into cash immediately in or\u00ad\nSale Starts Saturday, February 4,9 O'clock\nDon't stay away\u2014come to our store during this sale. There\nnever was such a feast of bargains. Think of it! Absolutely new\nand reliable goods being sold at from 25 to 50 per cent discount.\nAT THE BOSTON\nLadies and Misses Exclusive Outfitters. Union Block\nSilk and Wool Dresses\n4\n27.50 dresees, marked for\nwinter end sale at...\n30.00 dresses, your choice\nat winter-end sale...\n35.00 and slik dresses,\nat winter-end price...,\n40.00 and silk dresses,\nat winter-end sale at\n150 dresses\nOur store is the only place\nfor you to come and buy\nyour dresses\u2014we'll save\nyou money and time. You\ncan step into our store and\nget a dress to fit you, in all\nstyles and colors, for less\nmoney than it would cost\nyou to buy the material\nand make your own dress.\n14.50 wool dresses \"f AP\nwinter-end sale.. I\n.16.50 wool\ndresses\n18.50 wool\ndresses\n22.50 wool\ndresses\n24.50 w